{"tid":2198251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2男被控管有士巴拿和雷射筆罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-09-11T08:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T08:37:40.000Z","uid":356780,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8ea4d5e82656a6b078512913661ceff11c54bc","tid":2198251,"uid":356780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"日前報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200910/s00002/1599674523532/官-警「偏偏忘記」重要細節-裁藏噴漆激光筆男脫兩罪\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200910%2Fs00002%2F1599674523532%2F%E5%AE%98-%E8%AD%A6%E3%80%8C%E5%81%8F%E5%81%8F%E5%BF%98%E8%A8%98%E3%80%8D%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E8%A3%81%E8%97%8F%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E7%AD%86%E7%94%B7%E8%84%AB%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=3df0e6e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200910%2Fs00002%2F1599674523532%2F%E5%AE%98-%E8%AD%A6%E3%80%8C%E5%81%8F%E5%81%8F%E5%BF%98%E8%A8%98%E3%80%8D%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E8%A3%81%E8%97%8F%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E6%BF%80%E5%85%89%E7%AD%86%E7%94%B7%E8%84%AB%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA&h=d435256a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200910/s00002/1599674523532/官-警「偏偏忘記」重要細節-裁藏噴漆激光筆男脫兩罪</a><br />\n報稱地盤工程人員廖浩維（26歲）和資訊科技工程人員梁匡堯（24歲）被控去年10月27日在尖沙嘴彌敦道136號地下管有一支士巴拿，次被告另被控同日同地管有一支激光筆，案件昨於九龍裁判法院開審。當日拘捕次被告的警員鄧國輝（音譯）供稱，當日二人低頭急步繞過他和另一警員而行，「身體語言話畀我聽有可疑」，故截查二人。裁判官張天雁質疑：「唔繞過點經過你呢？唔通撞埋你嗰度呀？」<br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭<br />\n#張天雁裁判官<br />\n#裁決<br />\n#1027尖沙咀<br />\n<br />\nD1:廖 (26)<br />\nD2:梁 (24)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)D1管有物品意圖摧毀財產<br />\n(2)D2管有物品意圖摧毀財產<br />\n(3)D2管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n(1)D1被控於19年10月27日，在尖沙咀彌敦道136號地下外管有一把銀色扳手<br />\n(2)D2被控於同日同地管有一把銀色扳手<br />\n(3)D2被控於同日同地管有一支雷射筆連電芯<br />\n<br />\n速報<br />\n🥳全部罪名不成立🥳"},{"pid":"0e7f8f3ef62c782077c081e74ffa52fa548186b6","tid":2198251,"uid":356780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e56a63b6d8915fa4902e64ea0cdc0658e3a6c5","tid":2198251,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:26:32.000Z","msg":"如果唔係依家啲狗係唔係都拉正常應該連法庭都唔使上。"},{"pid":"9d05935fdff7d940fd82618b64d64775ca422470","tid":2198251,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"依d罪原本都應該告唔入但依家仲要睇邊個官判"},{"pid":"21dee6f35a1f457ee52025a5d7e128f9b0da46a1","tid":2198251,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"遇著蘇聞窿嘅話，一年半載都怕無走雞啦。"},{"pid":"4b30b0b5a3428d5a8b5e18edeff44a0e49623cb1","tid":2198251,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}